How to find the number is prime or not?

Best Method-

bool IsPrime(n)
{
  for(i=2;i<=Math.Sqrt(n);i++)
  {
    if(n%i==0) return false;
  }
  return true;
}

Time Complexity- O(sqrt(n))

Alternative Method 1-

bool IsPrime(n)
{
  for(i=2;i<=n;i++)
  {
    if(n%i==0) return false;
  }
  return true;
}

Time Complexity- O(n)


Alternative Method 2-

bool IsPrime(n)
{
  for(i=2;i<=n/2;i++)
  {
    if(n%i==0) return false;
  }
  return true;
}

Time Complexity- O(n)
